  {
    "title": "Trucage",
    "slug": "trucage",
    "client": "Independent",
    "role": "Director & Writer",
    "category": "documentary",
    "year": 2021,
    "vimeoId": "809385807",
    "thumbnail": "https://vumbnail.com/809385807.jpg",
    "description": "- Grand prix winner for the documentary category at VII Golden Baklava international student film festival in Turkey, 2022.\n\n\n- Golden Palm for the unique documentary subject at Saudi Film Festival, 2023\n\n\n- Got the 2nd rank out of 108 other international short films according to the audience vote in liftoff global film festival in UK, 2021.\n\n\n-Honorable mention at student world impact film festival U.S, 2022\n\n\n-Excellence trophy in the 2nd edition of the annual media forum in Egypt “faces of Egypt”, Sept 2021.\n\n\n- Official selection in the international competition of festival Internacional de cinema escolar de Alvorada in brazil, dec 2021.\n\n\n- Finalist in Meihodo international youth visual media festival in US, 2021\n\n\n- Finalist in the 5th international folklore film festival in India, Jan 2022.\n\n\n- Official selection in international Alexandria short film festival in Egypt, Feb 2022.\n\n\n- Official selection in Visions Cairo Egyptian short Film festival, 2023.\n\n\n- Official selection in Saudi film festival, may 2023.\n\n\n-Official selection in Africa international film festival in Nigeria, 2022.\n\n\n-Official selection in International interuniversity film festival in India, 2022.\n\n\n\n- Official selection in Ekurhuleni international film festival in south Africa, 2022.\n\n\n- 3 Awards winner in MSA star awards, 2021 (Best Film, Best directing, and best editing)\n\n\nA short documentary provides the realties of stunt profession featuring four professional stunts performers in Egyptian film industry as well as highlighting the importance of the stunt industry during the film production or other mediums, showing how integral stunt performer's roles are in producing content and showing the complexities of the stunt profession.",
    "featured": true,
    "credits": [
      {
        "role": "Director",
